    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## AVM Demo: WhatsApp -> AI -> CRM Pipeline\n\nThis workflow demonstrates AnyVision Media's AI-powered message processing:\n\n1. **Webhook** receives incoming WhatsApp messages\n2. **Claude AI** classifies message type (order/lead/inquiry/complaint)\n3. **Smart Router** sends each type down its own path\n4. **Orders**: AI extracts details -> Airtable CRM record -> confirmation\n5. **Leads**: AI scores 1-10 -> Airtable CRM record -> notification\n6. **Inquiries**: AI generates contextual reply\n7. **Complaints**: Auto-escalation with priority callback\n\n### Test with:\n```json\nPOST /webhook/whatsapp-incoming\n{\n  \"sender_name\": \"John Smith\",\n  \"phone\": \"+27821234567\",\n  \"message\": \"Hi, I'd like to order 5 branded videos for our product launch\"\n}\n```",
        "height": 480,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "d1a00001-0021-4000-8000-000000000021",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -100,
        120
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Orders Path\nAI extracts product, quantity, urgency\n-> Creates Airtable record\n-> Sends confirmation",
        "height": 160,
        "width": 300,
